        <Parent_String>centerpieces (furnishings) [300043082], furnishings by location or context [300037671], furnishings (works) [300037336], Furnishings (hierarchy name) [300037335], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
